{"id":43,"title":"问：什么是动态规划（DP）？适用于什么样的问题？","slug":"问：什么是动态规划（DP）？适用于什么样的问题？-1766595046","excerpt":"","content":"**参考回答：动态规划是一种利用最优子结构**和**重叠子问题**性质来求解问题的算法思想。它通过将原问题拆解为子问题，保存子问题的中间结果（避免重复计算），从而自底向上推导出最优解。使用动态规划需要满足无后效性（即当前子问题的最优解不受日后决策影响）和最优子结构等条件。典型应用场景包括：计算斐波那契数列（避免指数级重复计算）、路径规划（如网格最短路径或背包问题）、子序列问题（如最长递增子序列）等。动态规划的关键是在理解问题的状态转移方程，然后通过迭代或递归+记忆化求解。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.844903+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.844903+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f95d23c-2eec-8033-80a4-c28d35cdb6ad","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-20T05:56:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":43,"blog_post_id":43,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.601973+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.601973+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.844903+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:50:46.844903+08:00"}